text: Ilpo Nuolikivi (25 April 1942 - 7 July 2006) was a Finnish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:2006 deaths Category:Finnish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Finland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Hämeenlinna
